{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And sometimes they were 15-, 16-year-old boys, because they were-- it's-- it's-- it's unbelievable how, in no time, people can become inhumane, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It-- it-- it's a catching illness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It-- it's-- it shows that people need constant education and watch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You can't just let them go wild.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anyway, however, there were blockaltestes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember a-- a Polish lawyer from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was such a decent, nice chap who helped people and made sure if somebody wasn't quite well that he hid them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He told them, this man is today needed in the kitchen work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, there is two sides of the coin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There were very decent people who saved other people's lives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There were some who just, like the majority, they took care of themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And there were some very nasty ones.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This is the-- this is life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Anyway, so we were working there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The one interesting point is the camp was no different than many others.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We didn't have the cruelties of-- of that camp next to Buchenwald, Dora, where the German rockets were produced.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it was a terrible place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We knew about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when it came to Yom Kippur, strangely enough, the camp management, you know, the people who were in charge of the haftlinge, the-- the-- the inmates, arranged with the Germans that we can-- we can have our main meal on erev Yom Kippur, because we will not eat the next day.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then we can have something to eat in the evening, you know, which was quite tremendous considering what went on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So again, I'm trying to say that it was lucky in which camp you were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were people who-- who counted the days and they knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look, the English dates, we-- the-- not English dates.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
